[{"Id": 1020292, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "This Ziyarat is for taking oath of allegiance (Baiy’at) and for the renewal of covenant with the infallible Imams (a) who have narrated: “Performing our Ziyarat is equal to the renewal of covenant and pledge with us which is incumbent upon the people. Recite while performing the Ziyarat…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Yeh ziyarat baiy’at ke maaneend hai aur apni baiy’at ko taaza karne ke liye Imam’e Masoom (a) se riwaayat hai: Hamaari ziyarat karna ham se ahed aur baiy’at ko taaza karne ke bara-bar hai jo logo’n par laazim hai. Ziyarat karne ke waqt kahe…", "UrduDescription": "یہ  زیارت بیعت کے مانند ہے اور اپنی بیعت کو تازہ کرنے کے لئے امام معصومؑ سے روایت ہے: ہماری زیارت کرنا ہم سے عہد اور بیعت کو تازہ کرنے کے برابر ہے جو لوگوں پر لازم ہے۔ زیارت کرنے کہ وقت کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": 