tiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "As I am visiting you, O my master! Submissive to you, resorting to you, heading towards you, updating the covenant which Allah, Majestic and High be He, has taken regarding you on my neck, the covenant of your mastership and the disavowal of your enemies, confessing the obligation of your obedience.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "JEATOKA YAA MAWLAAYA ZAAA-ERAN LAKA WA MOSALLEMAN A’LAYKA WA LAAA-EZAN BEKA WA QAASEDAN ELAYKA OJADDEDO MAA AKHAZAHUL LAAHO A’ZZA WA JALLA LAKUM FEE RAQABATEE MENAL A’HDE WAL MEESAAQE BIL-WELAAYATE LAKUM WAL BARAAA-ATE MIN A-A’DAAA-EKUM MO’TAREFAN BIL-FARZE MIN TAA-A’TEKUM.", "ArabicText1": "جِئْتُكَ يَا مَوْلَايَ زَآئِرًا لَكَ وَمُسَلِّمًا عَلَيْكَ وَلَآئِذًا بِكَ وَقَاصِدًا اِلَيْكَ اُجَدِّدُ مَا اَخَذَهُ اللهُ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ لَكُمْ فِيْ رَقَبَتِيْ مِنَ الْعَهْدِ وَالْمِيْثَاقِ بِالْوِلَايَةِ لَكُمْ وَالْبَرَآءَةِ مِنْ اَعْدَآئِكُمْ مُعْتَرِفًا بِالْفَرْضِ مِنْ طَاعَتِكُمْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedS